metadata.name: Loopable Balloon RED
metadata.description:
Loopable Balloon is a collection of loopable GIFs of important characters in Crypto.

Loopable Balloon is a collection of loopable GIFs that pay homage to some of the most important characters in Crypto.  
With thanks to NyanBaloon, Nouns, Mfer, WolfGame, Cryptoadz, Rektguy and XCOPY for their amazing work.
